  "id": 9051520073979,
  "title": "FAPO LS Swap Long Tube Header 1-3/4  for Chevelle El Camino Malibu GTO Lemans",
  "handle": "fapo-ls-swap-long-tube-header-1-3-4-for-chevelle-el-camino-malibu-gto-lemans",
  "description": "<h4>Application</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Compatible with LS motor swap on 60-98 Chevy/GMC trucks (2WD)</li>\n<li>LS based engines: LS1, LS2, LS3, LS6, LS7, etc.</li>\n<li>Supported V8 engines: 4.8L, 5.3L, 5.7L, 6.0L, 6.2L</li>\n<li>1964 - 1977 Chevrolet Chevelle</li>\n<li>1964 - 1988 Chevrolet El Camino</li>\n<li>1970 - 1988 Chevrolet Monte Carlo</li>\n<li>1964 - 1988 Pontiac Lemans</li>\n<li>1964 - 1977 Pontiac GTO</li>\n<li>1977 - 1988 Pontiac Grand Prix</li>\n<li>1964 - 1977 Oldsmobile Cutlass</li>\n<li>1964 - 1972 Buick Skylark</li>\n<li>1978 - 1988 Buick Grand National</li>\n<li>1978 - 1988 Chevrolet Malibu</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Features</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Excellent quality and durability to improve vehicle performance, gains over 25+ rwhp</li>\n<li>Full length design for power gain from mid to high RPM range</li>\n<li>Fully mandrel bent tubes made of high quality 16-gauge 304 stainless steel</li>\n<li>Head flanges laser-cut from high quality 3/8-inch thick steel plates</li>\n<li>Flanges flattened by hydraulic press for precise, leak-free sealing</li>\n<li>Golden TIG brass-style welded joints to prevent cracking and wear</li>\n<li>Chrome-plated flanges for corrosion resistance</li>\n<li>Polished surface for extra protection against rusting</li>\n<li>Includes all accessories shown in photos</li>\n<li>1-year warranty for any manufacturing defect</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Technical Specifications</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<strong>Header Type:</strong> Long Tube / Full Length</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Primary Diameter:</strong> 1-3/4 in.</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Collector Diameter:</strong> 3 in. (76mm)</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Head Flange Thickness:</strong> 3/8 in. (9.5mm)</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Pipe Thickness:</strong> 16 gauge (1.5mm)</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Material:</strong> 304 Stainless Steel</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Finish:</strong> Polished</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Notes</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Will NOT fit LS4 engines</li>\n<li>Will NOT work on 4WD/4x4 models</li>\n<li>Will NOT work on standard SBC or BBC engines</li>\n<li>Will NOT install with factory column shift linkage</li>\n<li>May require special motor mounts for clearance</li>\n<li>May require angled spark plug boots for tight clearance</li>\n<li>If using larger 4L80E or older THM 350/400 automatic transmissions, the bellhousing ears may need trimming for proper clearance</li>\n</ul>",
